<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>πρὸ μὲν πάντων 

    <lb n="2"/>πολλὰ προσαγορεύω 

    <lb n="3"/>τὴν σὴν μητρικὴν 

    <lb n="4"/>διάθεσιν καὶ <choice><corr>τὰς</corr><sic>της</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="5"/><choice><corr>εὐλαβεστάτας</corr><sic>ευλαβεσταταις</sic></choice> μου 

    <lb n="6"/>ἀδελφὰς <choice><corr>Θεοτίμαν</corr><sic>θεοτιμα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ <choice><corr>Ταρίλλαν</corr><sic>ταριλλα</sic></choice>. επεις<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="8"/><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> ὅτι ὠλιγώ-

    <lb n="9"/>ρησας δι᾽ ἐμὲ ὅτι 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>ἐξῆλθον</corr><sic>εξηλθα</sic></choice> ἐκ τοῦ 

    <lb n="11"/>μοναστηρίου Ἄπα 

    <lb n="12"/>Σαρους. ὠλιγώρη-

    <lb n="13"/>σα οὖν. πέμπουσίν 

    <lb n="14"/>με εἰς τὸ <choice><corr>πραιτώ-

    <lb n="15"/>ριον</corr><sic>πραιτωριν</sic></choice> καθάπαξ 

    <lb n="16"/>πρὸς τὸν κόμι-

    <lb n="17"/>τα καὶ καθ᾽ ὥρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αν</unclear> 

    <lb n="18"/>γράφω ἐπιστο-

    <lb n="19"/>λὴν ἐν τάξει νο-

    <lb n="20"/>ταρίων. διὰ τοῦτο 

    <lb n="21"/><choice><corr>ἀπέστην</corr><sic>απεστη</sic></choice> ἐκ τῶν 

    <lb n="22"/>οἴκει, ἕως οὗ ἂν 

    <lb n="23"/><choice><corr>συντάσσωσίν</corr><sic>συντασσουσιν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="24"/>με ὅτι οὐκέτι 

    <lb n="25"/>ἀναγκάζουσίν 

    <lb n="26"/>σε καὶ ἤνεγκ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> 

    <lb n="27"/>με πάλιν εἰς 

    <lb n="28"/>τὸν αὐτὸν <choice><corr>τόπον</corr><sic>τοπων</sic></choice>. 

    <lb n="29"/>μὴ οὖν ὀλιγω-

    <lb n="30"/>ρήσατε δι᾽ ἐμὲ 

    <lb n="31"/>ὅλως, ἀλλὰ 

    <lb n="32"/>μνημονεύσατέ 

    <lb n="33"/>με ἐν τῇ εὐχῇ 

    <lb n="34"/><choice><corr>ὑμῶν</corr><sic>ημων</sic></choice>. δὸς οὖν 

    <lb n="35"/>τὸ <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>μοζίκιον</corr><sic>μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ζικιν</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected">μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ζ</unclear>ζικιν</del></subst> μου 

    <lb n="36"/>αὐτῷ. ποίησον 

    <lb n="37"/>καὶ τὸ καταπέ-

    <lb n="38"/>τασμα καὶ τὴν 

    <lb n="39"/><space dim="horizontal" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> στολήν μου. </ab></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="600" notBefore="501" type="textDate">VI</date></p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Vgl. APF 50, 2004, S. 187f.</p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">43</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3150</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">35941</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">43</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3150</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;43;3150" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Plate XII</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Mandilaras, Papyroi (1980), 66, S. 198 und (1994), 68, S. 419</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.35941" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH7efb90521b9394d260825e"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>